A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 State and Local Finance – Use of Funds – Prohibition
3 FOR the purpose of prohibiting a county or municipality and certain units of a county or
4 municipality from using public funds to provide funding or payments to a certain
5 organization; prohibiting an officer or unit of State government from using any
6 appropriation to provide funding or payments to a certain organization; prohibiting
7 certain organizations that receive public funds from a county or municipality or
8 funds appropriated by the State from using those funds to provide funding for or
9 payment to a certain organization; and generally relating to the use of public funds
10 and funds appropriated by the State.
